Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.42,银日文-ja,,0,0,0,,じゃ あしたから４時起きにすっか
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:20.44,Spoon_Main,Gramps,0,0,0,,Then let's start your day at \N4 AM beginning tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.44,0:00:22.66,Spoon_Main,H,0,0,0,,Oh, please no.
