Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.76,0:00:27.58,Spoon_Main,MD,0,0,0,,Damn you, farmhand!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.35,银日文-ja,,0,0,0,,己 バイト
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.48,0:00:31.78,银日文-ja,,0,0,0,,それしきの働きっぷりで俺が認めると思うなよ
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.58,0:00:31.91,Spoon_Main,MD,0,0,0,,Don't think I'll accept you \Njust because you work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:33.24,银日文-ja,,0,0,0,,父さん 邪魔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.91,0:00:32.97,Spoon_Main,M,0,0,0,,Dad, you're in the way.
